        , 14: [ {class: "vs", text: "Learn where is wisdom, where is strength, where is understanding; that you may know also where is length of days, and life, where is the light of the eyes, and peace."} ]
        , 15: [ {class: "vs", text: "Who has found out her place? and who has come into her treasuries?"} ]
        , 16: [ {class: "vs", text: "Where are the princes of the heathen, and such as ruled the beasts that are upon the earth;"} ]
        , 17: [ {class: "vs", text: "those who had their pastime with the fowls of the air, and those who hoarded up silver and gold, wherein men trust; and of whose getting there is no end?"} ]
        , 18: [ {class: "vs", text: "For those who made in silver, and were so careful, and whose works are past finding out,"} ]
