        , 22: [ {class: "vs", text: "It has not been heard of in Canaan, neither has it been seen in Teman."} ]
        , 23: [ {class: "vs", text: "The sons also of Agar that seek understanding, which are in the land, the merchants of Merran and Teman, and the authors of fables, and the searchers out of understanding; none of these have known the way of wisdom, or remembered her paths."} ]
